source.name: Wireless Hot Spot in Washington DC
source.description: Wireless Hot Spot locations. The dataset contains locations and attributes of Wireless Hot Spots, created as part of the DC Geographic Information System (DC GIS) for the D.C. Office of the Chief Technology Officer (OCTO) and participating D.C. government agencies.
